* {{ill|Ajima Shrine|ja|味鋺神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ajima Shrine|qq=}} ({{ill|Aichi Prefecture|ja|愛知県|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Aichi Prefecture|qq=}}, {{ill|Nagoya|ja|名古屋市|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nagoya|qq=}}): Located near the Ajima Kofun Group.
* {{ill|Isonokami Jingu|lt=Isonokami Jingu|lt=Isonokami Shrine|ja|石上神宮|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Isonokami Shrine|qq=}} ({{ill|Nara Prefecture|ja|奈良県|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nara Prefecture|qq=}}, {{ill|Tenri|ja|天理市|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenri|qq=}}): Founded after the transfer of the Futsumitama Sword, which Umashimaji enshrined.
